description: "Apologies, dear friend... but can I take a moment of your time to preach our home and protector, Mother Nature? Earth is rotting-the time for action is now. Reduce, reuse, and recucle material wastes! #Be a part of the solution, not the pollution"
about: A flame has awoken in the dark abyss. For ages eternal, it has raged as an insurmountable inferno-a savage beast that beckons in its every waking moment for sustenance. To quell the undying storm, I, as the jailer of this aberration, must feed it memes
